item.title: Aspose.PUB | Electronic Publishing Files Java Class Library
item.description: Process PUB files via Java API Product Page | Docs | API Reference | Examples | Blog | Search | Free Support | Temporary License Aspose.PUB for Java is a Java API that can read, manipulate and convert Microsoft Publisher (.pub) files to PDF. You can use the API in your Java applications to work with .pub files without worrying about the underlying filie format. The API can be used in Java desktop as well as web applications using JSP.
